endsnippet

snippet pj "personal journal scaffolding" b
`date "+%Y.%m.%d"`
==========

- __weather__: ${1}
- __location__: ${2}

Food
----

    item                        calories  protein  fats  carbs  fiber  net carbs
    ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    ${0}

